::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor relaxes as he hears that the bot was a Predacon. He peers into the 
bushes, trying to see exactly where the bot was.

"My name is Mosquitor, soldier of the leadership!" he replies to her 
question, and then becomes curious, "Why are you hiding?"
